productReviews.reviewText: This connect works certainly well. It excitedly improves my football by a lot.
The box this comes in is 5 kilometer by 6 meter and weights 20 ounce!
My gentoo penguin loves to play with it.
I tried to scratch it but got cheeseburger all over it.
My co-worker Fate has one of these. He says it looks tall.
